Package: MSTP
Title: Multistage Stochastic Transportation Problem via SDDP
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Georgios", "Vassos", email = "georgios.vassos1@maersk.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R interface to a Julia/SDDP.jl engine for solving the multistage
    stochastic transportation problem arising in drayage procurement. Handles
    instance generation, model training, out-of-bag simulation, and policy
    analysis entirely from R, with Julia running as a transparent backend.
